Feature: Staff Reject Application in the Queue

Staff = SA, PC, CTPO, Trainee

@orv2-2474
Rule: Staff can reject an application

@orv2-2474
Rule: Staff must input a reason for rejection

@orv2-2474
Rule: The reason for rejection is date / time stamped when saved

@orv2-2474
Rule: The reason for rejection is IDIR username stamped when saved

@orv2-2474
Rule: A rejected application becomes an application in progress

@orv2-2474
Rule: The CV Client is notified via email when a application is approvrejecteded

@orv2-2474
Rule: The elapsed time in queue stops counting when a application is rejected
